snippet.title: Shantae: Risky's Revenge Official iOS Trailer
snippet.description:
Your wish is granted! Shantae shakes her hips, whips her hair back and forth, and transforms into magical creatures in this action quest game from WayForward. Get it now on iPhone, iPad, iPod Touch, Nintendo DSi, Nintendo DSiXL, and Nintendo 3DS.

For more information check out http://www.wayforward.com
Shantae: Risky's Revenge is available in the iTunes Store!
Make sure to Subscribe and follows us on these sites
